@WinterArcApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:8080

### Register User
POST {{WinterArcApi_HostAddress}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123"
}

###

### Login
POST {{WinterArcApi_HostAddress}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "password": "SecurePassword123"
}

###

### Get All Goals
GET {{WinterArcApi_HostAddress}}/goals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create Goal
POST {{WinterArcApi_HostAddress}}/goals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Exercise Daily",
  "description": "Go for a 30-minute run",
  "xpReward": 150
}

###

### Update Goal
PUT {{WinterArcApi_HostAddress}}/goals/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Exercise Daily - Updated",
  "isCompleted": true
}

###

### Delete Goal
DELETE {{WinterArcApi_HostAddress}}/goals/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create Check-In
POST {{WinterArcApi_HostAddress}}/goals/1/checkins
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "note": "Completed 5k run today!"
}

###

### Get User Overview
GET {{WinterArcApi_HostAddress}}/me/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
